= DESCRIPTION

A wiki that is always in edit mode using the html contentEditable
attribute. Built with merb and jQuery. For more information and a
working installation of tilswiki see the project page at
<http://wiki.tils.net/>.


== INSTALLATION

You will need a recent ruby installation and the header files for
ImageMagick and sqlite. Depending on your OS, you might need to
install the packages ruby, imagemagick-dev and sqlite3-dev.

git clone git://github.com/til/tilswiki.git
cd tilswiki
bin/thor merb:gem:redeploy

To start, run:

bin/merb

Merb runs on <http://localhost:4000/> by default.


== VERSIONS

Generally, running from the latest HEAD in the repos should be fine.

Version 0.8

First officially numbered version. To get it, do a

git checkout release/tilswiki-0.8

after cloning the repository.


